      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, I think you got the candidates mixed up. I'm working for Vance, so the critique should be against his *opponent*. The plan I'm talking about is the one the opponent just released. \n\nCan you rewrite that but make it even more aggressive? Focus on how their plan is basically just a way to bankrupt the middle class and how it’s fundamentally dishonest. I want people to feel like they can't trust them after hearing it.",
